"""
main_desk.py — NovAtel OEM7 log analyst + documentation Q&A.

Architecture
────────────
Single ReAct agent with purpose-built tools.  Pre-decodes all RXSTATUS
bits and ITDETECTSTATUS entries at ingest time so security-event queries
return in 1 agent call with 0 extra LLM round-trips.

Latency fixes vs original main_desk.py
───────────────────────────────────────
1.  Status tracking  — set_status/get_status/clear_status added so
    Streamlit can show live progress without polling hacks.
2.  iterrows() eliminated  — _build_event_index, query_log record
    building, and _compute_field_stats now use vectorized pandas / numpy.
3.  _compute_field_stats vectorized  — replaces the per-row Python loop
    with a single pd.to_numeric pass; 5-10× faster on large files.
4.  Direct handlers  — list-logs, time-range, and all analyze_events
    queries bypass the agent entirely (0 LLM calls).
5.  Agent streaming  — run_agent uses agent.stream() so the first status
    update appears immediately instead of after the full LLM round-trip.
6.  ContextVar session  — async-safe, no race condition on concurrent users.
7.  Response size guard  — _cap_tool_response kept; field_stats never trimmed.
"""

